product.productName: Gatorade Frost Thirst Quencher Powder, Glacier Freeze 76.5 oz.
product.shortDescription:
• Glacier Freeze flavor, 76.5-ounce powder makes 9 gallons
  • When you sweat, you lose more than water, Gatorade Thirst Quencher contains critical electrolytes to help replace what’s lost in sweat
  • Top off your fuel stores with carbohydrate energy, your body's preferred source of fuel
  • Tested in the lab and used by the pros
  • One serving makes 12 fl oz when mixed with water
product.longDescription:
Replenish Lost Electrolytes

The harder you work to win, the more sweat you lose. This sweat contains more than just water - it has essential electrolytes such as sodium and potassium. These elements play a key role in helping your body regulate fluid level balance. Significant losses in fluids and electrolytes can negatively impact performance, especially during long bouts of training. Gatorade Thirst Quencher Powder is scientifically researched and game-tested to replenish these lost electrolytes, hydrating better than water and trusted by some of the world’s best athletes.

Fuel Your Performance

To stay at the top of your game, your body needs the right fuel. Gatorade Thirst Quencher is scientifically formulated with carbohydrates, the body’s preferred source of energy. This allows you to maintain your performance level, letting you bring the heat all game long. Whether you play soccer, baseball, volleyball, or any other sport, Gatorade will help you stay hydrated and bring the energy needed to compete.

Convenient and Versatile

Gatorade Glacier Freeze 76.5-ounce powder is not only perfect for athletes, but it's also great to store in your cooler or sports bottle when going camping, hitting the beach, tailgating at the big game, having a picnic, or enjoying the great outdoors. Simply add water to the Gatorade Thirst Quencher Powder, stir, and you're ready to hydrate. Beat the heat and stay hydrated with Gatorade Thirst Quencher.

properties.key_features_sams: Made with a cut-resistant and grease-resistant design

properties.marketing_message: Our strongest disposable paper plate, Member's Mark® Ultra Plate, 10-1/16" (204 ct.), features a grease and cut-resistant coating with advanced soak protection so that even the sauciest meals won't leak through. And because these disposable plates are our strongest and largest, they're tough enough for foodservice industry use and for hefty, often messy meals, like barbecue. This large, 204-pack of strong paper plates is perfect for stocking up so that you always have some on hand. Where, When and How Can I Use Heavy-Duty Paper Plates? Whether you're planning a backyard cookout for a family reunion and need some extra plates or are brainstorming rainy-day crafts you can make with your kiddo with inexpensive items you can find around the house, these made-in-the-USA, Member's Mark Ultra Plates are the solution. Practical (and Some Creative) Uses for Heavy-Duty Paper Plates: Holding hors d'oeuvres at your next bash Safeguarding bowls in the microwave to prevent splatter Making cleanup a breeze by eliminating a pile of dishes Extra padding between ceramic dishes when you're moving Being a makeshift paint palette for your little painter during craft time Staying strong for a pile of messy barbecue during backyard cookouts Are Disposable Paper Plates Good for Crafting? Yes, disposable paper plates are an affordable and suitable material for crafting with your kiddo. Because they're thicker than the average paper plate, our strong paper plates are a great alternative to construction paper. Take disposable paper plate crafting to the next level by turning these fancy paper plates into even fancier animals. All you need is Member's Mark Ultra Plates, scissors, construction paper, glue, markers or crayon and a little imagination. Try making a snake, swan, cat or fish with your little crafter.

properties.marketing_message: Make your meals stand out with McCormick® Poultry Gravy Mix. It's wonderful for adding rich flavor to chicken and turkey. Why Use McCormick Poultry Gravy Mix? McCormick Poultry Gravy Mix is made with enriched wheat flour, spices and chicken broth. It's free of artificial flavors and MSG. This gravy mix comes in a convenient plastic container with a sectioned lid that allows you to easily sprinkle or spoon out the contents onto food. It's ideal for use in homes and in restaurants. The label on the container also has recipes on the back. How Do I Make McCormick Poultry Gravy? You can make this gravy mix with ease. It offers a homemade taste and makes preparing your dishes hassle-free. Just follow the directions on the container and add water as needed into a saucepan. Next, heat and stir to create a delicious sauce to pour over foods like mashed potatoes, sandwiches and stuffing. Delectable Recipes with McCormick's Poultry Gravy Mix Aside from enjoying this gravy as it is, you can use it as an ingredient for an array of recipes. Make a chicken pot pie by adding this gravy mix into a skillet of milk, water and butter. Bring to boil; stir in frozen vegetables and pre-cooked, cubed chicken. Place store-bought or homemade biscuit dough on bottom of a baking dish, and bake for eight minutes. Pour mixture on top, cover with more biscuit dough, and bake in the oven for 20 minutes Cook up delicious burgers by combining this sauce with ground turkey, minced onions and parsley Add onions, mushrooms, butter, turkey or chicken pan drippings to the prepared gravy mix to enhance the flavor Create a chowder by combining it with half-and-half, cooked turkey or chicken chunks, a can of whole corn, sliced bacon, chopped onions, flour, sage and red potatoes

product.productName: Marathon Multifold 1-Ply White Paper Towels 16 pks., 250 towels/pk
product.longDescription:
Marathon® Multifold Paper Towels are designed to fit a wide range of dispensers. They are ideal for a variety of facilities including government and public buildings, Class A office buildings, lodging, and restaurants. These premium multifold towels deliver reliable performance at a low cost per use. They are stackable for use in an open tray, on the counter, or loaded in a wall-mounted dispenser, making them highly versatile. The Marathon® Multifold Paper Towels are responsibly made and can help earn LEED® credits. They contain at least 40% post-consumer recycled fiber and are Sustainable Forestry Initiative® certified. The SFI® sourcing label is proof Georgia-Pacific is using fiber from responsible and legal sources. SFI® is a registered trademark owned by Sustainable Forestry Initiative, Inc. www.sfiprogram.org. Your guests, tenants, patients, or customers will appreciate the quality while you enjoy the savings.

Marathon® toilet paper, paper towels, napkins and soaps provide businesses with quality products for restrooms, break rooms, and other applications. Designed for use in offices, restaurants, healthcare, industrial, educational, daycare and other facilities, Marathon® products combine quality and value in a variety of styles that offer cost-effective solutions for businesses.

GP PRO is a division of Georgia-Pacific Consumer Products. We deliver well-designed, durable and easy-to-maintain professional solutions to meet the handwashing and cleaning needs for a range of business applications.
